name: Warrior Style Concept
description:

To maximize its effectiveness, consider using relevant tags such as:

armor, solo, weapon, holding weapon, helmet, shoulder armor, mask, full body,

This embedding works really well with my DarkRevPikas model, but it should work well with other models as well.

The recommended settings are:

CFG Scale: 5-7

Steps: 20-40
